法領導ＢＬＭ，就係美民主黨最想像唔到，多少，佢哋以為利用依班人加上媒體可以將ＢＬＭ控制係佢哋想要嘅範圍，最好就係不斷有警民衝突畫面，更易於羅列更多罪名俾侵或共和黨。<br />\n<br />\n但ＢＬＭ已經變成「國定周末搶掠日」"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T19:26:10.000Z","msg":"今日19好文:<br />\n<br />\n<em>西方對於兩股思潮，只懂防範一樣，卻擁抱另一樣，因為社會主義主張國際化、平等、包容；而納粹由第一日起就是排斥，然後是仇恨。<br />\n<br />\n但是社會主義到極端也一樣是仇恨。只是他們病情發作時，一樣的咆哮、一樣變成面目扭曲的喪屍。他們到了那一刻，包括美國的 BLM 反杜林普的暴動分子，和中國的小粉紅，覺得自己在崛起、是何等的理直氣壯；他們都永遠覺得自己在替天行道，是崇高的 人，而不是喪屍。</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/09/02/socialist-and-nazist/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2020%2F09%2F02%2Fsocialist-and-nazist%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hYm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=87f4dc0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/09/02/socialist-and-nazist/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T00:00:02.000Z","msg":"鄧小平改革開放時期：要警惕右，但主要是防止『左』<br />\n(背景有班共產黨阻撚住佢)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當今聖上左右都剷除晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22056408009ca023a9d8ac6ab97c582b0f642188","tid":2186124,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1641747074d12ebd8d5af4d281e26a847ee3b9c7","tid":2186124,"uid":218,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"cf4851298b5af07a60dcd41b71ba63dbc407c483","tid":2186124,"uid":41087,"like":131,"dislike":4,"score":127,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T18:34:54.000Z","msg":"即刻多幾個黑鬼老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T19:00:48.000Z","msg":"笑咗 係咪要落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T00:01:02.000Z","msg":"厚德村<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8fc1ded8067bac10d2d11995f40482946973a1e","tid":2186124,"uid":165772,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T00:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/McGoGsn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMcGoGsn.png&h=9aa7e03