領導ＢＬＭ，就係美民主黨最想像唔到，多少，佢哋以為利用依班人加上媒體可以將ＢＬＭ控制係佢哋想要嘅範圍，最好就係不斷有警民衝突畫面，更易於羅列更多罪名俾侵或共和黨。<br />\n<br />\n但ＢＬＭ已經變成「國定周末搶掠日」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ni agree with you to a large extend, and i think it ultimately boils down to the means, not the end of the movement. Everyone knows what BLM is fighting for, but the ways how protesters engage in the movement speak evidently for their civility. I guess Hong Kong protesters could be a prime example in regard to that. <br />\n<br />\nBut again, I am not there. I aint even american so i couldnt really speak for them - other than how i see it."},{"pid":"b8c50b9e9981d7ca82f8b2593f676a70216b8fbc","tid":2186124,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T01:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0db9674309ca87572209f3002cf827871d5d92","tid":2186124,"uid":55080,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T01:40:15.000Z","msg":"Please stay Messi<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1486abd4a4e7520fd3f97deabbe0c4b01060c5","tid":2186124,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T01:46:53.000Z","msg":"係BLM 橫行下，嫁個黑人即刻生意滔滔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12a4571c4cd8d391860451470fd0b9aa5919502","tid":2186124,"uid":230054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T01:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2e2c571465959465007b4c74b1a46818ac4933","tid":2186124,"uid":183217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:33:09.000Z","msg":"文化大革命 遲早公開吊死平民／商人"},{"pid":"6dc2642ed1088da28fa7bc167af0224be0bba350","tid":2186124,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:50:09.0